query:
SELECT id, name, description, date, time 
FROM trip_routes 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
AND (name LIKE '%Štrbské Pleso, Kúpeľná%' OR name LIKE '%Jasna Demanovska Dolina%')
ORDER BY date;
